message: I propose a 60/40 split in my favor. It's a strong opening offer, but time is money Bob!
Let's be fair. This is a more equitable split, and it gives us both a healthy starting point.  Time is money, but we can't forget about a fair share!
Bob, I appreciate the sentiment of fairness, but I need to look out for my own interests too. This is my counter-offer.  It's a good deal considering the time pressure.
